	<h3 class="heading header-reset">About T. H. Baker</h3>
	<p>T. H. Baker is a family owned business with over 125 years experience in the jewellery and watch industry. T. H. Baker has established itself as a popular independent jeweller while sticking to standards that have been set since its beginning in 1888.</p>
	<p>T. H. Baker operates in over 20 stores located throughout the Midlands and southern England. Each store has its own dedicated team of reliable and knowledgeable staff to help customers with an elite level of customer service.</p>
